<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.6.1">
<l>nāvalam periya tīviṉil vāḻum</l>
<l rend="indent">naṅkaimīr kāḷitō raṟputam kēḷīr</l>
<l>tūvalam puriyu ṭaiyati rumāl</l>
<l rend="indent">tūyavā yilkuḻa lōcaiva ḻiyē</l>
<l>kōvalar ciṟumi yariḷaṅ koṅkai</l>
<l rend="indent">kutukalip pavuṭa luḷaviḻn teṅkum</l>
<l>kāvaluṅ kaṭantu kayiṟu mālai</l>
<l rend="indent">yākivan tukaviḻn tuniṉṟa ṉarē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Ladies living in the great country of Nāvalam!</l>
<l rend="indent">Listen to this miracle,</l>
<l>The way the flute sounds upon the pure lips of Tirumāl,</l>
<l rend="indent">with the pure right-whorled conch!</l>
<l>Everywhere, the cowherd girls’ bodies and minds fade</l>
<l rend="indent">as [their] young breasts rejoice,</l>
<l>Escaping their guardians, they come as a threaded garland,</l>
<l rend="indent">shyly bowing their heads.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
